What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Hydrolysed Collagen Market?



Market Analysis and Size

The global hydrolyzed collagen market is expected to grow significantly during the forecast period because of increasing demand for convenience food and growing awareness regarding hydrolyzed collagen globally. As consumers become progressively aware of the health benefits of beverages, it may increase the demand for hydrolyzed collagen drinks. Hydrolyzed collagen-based drinks are high in arginine, hydroxyproline, amino acids glycine, and proline, associated with cell regeneration, energy supply, and metabolism.

